真係有文話唔洗戴咩，有冇link？定係佢地只係quote WHO advice / authority statements / news report 好多鬼佬都係後者，然後就claim口罩冇用云云。

我淨係睇過兩篇。

一篇係講patient study, patient戴左可以有效防止自己嘅virus particle shedding出口罩外面 。姐係「防傳染比人」。（https://lm.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpubmed%2F23505369%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1queAc09dsSy_T1RcgLi23vmQUrbpanT9sAo_Bs9CXmeHvV4V2cRQEy8M&h=AT1xFVlPgBGAT7D0DXg4mL2Qqn6CoyRo20g1qzbx70EcHS1x25t9U3pNSs0QiQ-EjVs74LQXh0c9maZeAxVt7o9y9dHZMHOA1KN5UAEehLc-mNW2DckClYEjcLKabR5OYuQuFA37awPY8sTqep6L53yjAgBhLJKFCodL7-IA0Q）

另一篇係exposure study （https://www.ijidonline.com/article/S1201-9712(08)01008-4/fulltext?fbclid=IwAR3prLrRkOflvc8OFWqg1gGJYxPHqhOGaJT93b0le4foDrnBlIlS3gxXagA），講如果健康嘅家庭成員戴左口罩，會唔會比自己患有流感 + 一齊住嘅小朋友傳染到。結果係用正確方法戴口罩嘅人係significantly提升「防比人傳染」嘅機會


Results: We recruited 286 adults with exposure to respiratory infections in the Australian winters of 2006 and 2007 - 94 adults were randomized to surgical masks, 90 to P2 masks and 102 to the control group. Using intention to treat analysis, we found no significant difference in the relative risk of respiratory illness in the mask groups compared to control group. However, compliance with mask use was less than 50%. In an adjusted analysis of compliant subjects, masks as a group had protective efficacy in excess of 80% against clinical influenza-like illness. The efficacy against proven viral infection and between P2 masks (57%) and surgical masks (33%) was non-significant.


我淨係睇左abstract 冇睇內文。所以幾奇怪，真係有文話口罩冇用@@？

定係純粹係以下嘅argument：
1. 「防傳比人」 比「防比人傳 」更有效。所以，「防比人傳」係冇效的。（邏輯錯哂，屌都廢事）

2. 用錯誤方法戴口罩會增加感染風險。所以，戴口罩無法防止被病毒感染。（oh diu，所以procedure做錯左就代表件product本身冇用？）
